data.description: This impressive 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts over 1800 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space. Located along a serene freshwater canal, it offers the perfect blend of elegance & comfort, both inside & out. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by cathedral ceilings & natural light. The great room, seamlessly connected to the kitchen, forms the heart of this residence. The kitchen has ample cabinets, countertops, & stainless-steel appliances. The master bedroom is a spacious retreat with walk-in closets & a luxurious master bathroom. It features a separate shower, soaking tub, & dual sinks, providing a serene space for relaxation.Two guest bedrooms, situated on the opposite side of the home, offer privacy & comfort. They share a well-appointed guest bathroom, perfect for accommodating family & friends.Step onto the oversized lanai, a perfect spot for outdoor entertaining. This property's location along a freshwater canal adds to its appeal. Enjoy the peaceful sights and sounds of the water while sipping morning coffee or fishing from your private spot. Connected to city water and sewer. It's also conveniently located near dining and shopping, making daily life a breeze.
